# Book Management API

## Books [/api/v1/books]

### Get All Books [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "data": [
            { "id": 1, "title": "Book A", "author": "Author A" }
          ],
          "meta": { "timestamp": "2026-01-01T12:00:00" }
        }

### Create Book [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "title": "New Book",
          "author": "Author X"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

---

## Book Detail [/api/v1/books/{book_id}]

+ Parameters
    + book_id: 1 (number)

### Get Book [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

### Delete Book [DELETE]

+ Response 204

---

## Users [/api/v1/users]

### Get Users [GET]

+ Response 200

### Create User [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "username": "john",
          "email": "john@example.com"
        }

+ Response 201

---

## Reviews [/api/v1/book-reviews]

### Get Reviews [GET]

+ Response 200

### Create Review [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "rating": 5,
          "comment": "Great",
          "book_id": 1,
          "user_id": 1
        }

+ Response 201